		<h2>Welcome</h2>
		<p>You are invited to be part of our church family!</p>
		<p>San Antonio Mennonite Church is an open, family-friendly, singles-friendly church. Children are an important part of our family and are included in the worship service.</p>
		<p>Our worship focuses on God's presence with us. Our preaching is centered on Christ and the Bible.</p>
		<p>We are committed to serve those in need, to speak out against injustice, and to work for reconciliation between all people.</p>
		<p>We are committed to share the hope we have in Christ and invite everyone into our Christian community.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="section_statements">
		<h2>Vision Statement</h2>
		<p>	Our vision is to be a caring community,<br/>
			being transformed by Christ's love<br/>
			so that we share God's peace with all people.
		</p>
		<h2>Mission Statement</h2>
		<p>	Our mission is to embody and proclaim the Good News of Jesus to our neighbor,<br/>
			while growing in an abiding relationship with Christ and fellow believers.
		</p>
